<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idefb13ee1-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s3813"><num value="3813">§ 3813.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are hereby authorized to be appropriated such sums as may be necessary to carry out the provisions of this chapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idefb13ee2-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/pl/96/468/s13">Pub. L. 96–468, § 13</ref>, formerly § 14, <date date="1980-10-17">Oct. 17, 1980</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/94/2234">94 Stat. 2234</ref>; renumbered § 13, <ref href="/us/pl/104/127/tIX/s914/b/2">Pub. L. 104–127, title IX, § 914(b)(2)</ref>, <date date="1996-04-04">Apr. 4, 1996</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/110/1186">110 Stat. 1186</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
