<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="idefb13ee4-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="priorProvisions" id="idefb13ee5-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Prior Provisions</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">A prior <ref href="/us/pl/96/468/s13">section 13 of Pub. L. 96–468</ref> was renumbered section 12 and is classified to <ref href="/us/usc/t7/s3812">section 3812 of this title</ref>.</p>
